    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beer Factory 是一款模拟经营和管理类游戏。接受挑战，做好对自己的啤酒厂、员工、生产线，及货物的进出口管理工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>物流管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/28c9895f02f230def3da58bd04d14a78.poster.avif?t=1753024599\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/28c9895f02f230def3da58bd04d14a78.webm?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/28c9895f02f230def3da58bd04d14a78.mp4?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制造业通常需要一条生产线、某些资源，存储选项以及运输。在Beer Factory 游戏中，你工作的目标是出产啤酒，你需要进口和储存原材料、提炼、在罐中酿制、储存啤酒、装瓶，最终交到客户手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>招聘和管理雇员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/2bae9df3ae233db64e04be5960b7173b.poster.avif?t=1753024599\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/2bae9df3ae233db64e04be5960b7173b.webm?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/2bae9df3ae233db64e04be5960b7173b.mp4?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有什么会比雇用员工帮你完成日常工作更能有效提高业务的方法了。工厂里的员工们可以处理大多数工作，但你要指挥他们该怎么做。记得时刻监督他们的工作进展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现实的经济</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/dd8171fe1c19e2ed574d05dc2bfaab8c.poster.avif?t=1753024599\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/dd8171fe1c19e2ed574d05dc2bfaab8c.webm?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/dd8171fe1c19e2ed574d05dc2bfaab8c.mp4?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个行动都会产生成本，这与你对财务方面的管理工作息息相关。从招聘到运输再到税收，Beer Factory 游戏中的整个财务系统被设计得尽可能地接近现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>定制及升级工厂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/ef1077703d49282a807bd3c3a84ddb30.poster.avif?t=1753024599\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/ef1077703d49282a807bd3c3a84ddb30.webm?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782570/extras/ef1077703d49282a807bd3c3a84ddb30.mp4?t=1753024599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要各种设备酿制啤酒。投资了新的机器后，你就可以使用它、改进它，并利用它的最大生产能力产出更多的商品！随即扩大工厂，使其不断得到成长，让你的商业向帝国式的方向发展！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 韩语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
